Package: rD3plot
Type: Package
Version: 1.0.9
Date: 2021-04-07
Title: Interactive Networks, Timelines, Barplots, Galleries with 'R'
Description: Creates interactive analytic graphs with 'R'. It joins the data analysis power of R and the visualization libraries of JavaScript in one package. The package provides interactive networks, timelines, barplots, image galleries and evolving networks. Graphs are represented as D3 graphs embedded in a web page ready for its interactive analysis and exploration.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: igraph (>= 1.0.1)
Suggests: shiny
